episodes.title: L&P EXCLUSIVE: The Cult of the Real Housewives | TLC Docuseries Interview
episodes.description:
L&P EXCLUSIVE — Lenox & Parker Editor-in-Chief Christal Jordan sits down with filmmaker Julian P. Hobbs and Executive Producer Deniese Davis to discuss The Cult of the Real Housewives, the highly anticipated documentary event premiering January 1 on TLC.

This revealing conversation explores the cultural impact, celebrity obsession, power dynamics, and psychological grip behind one of the most influential reality TV franchises of all time. From fandom to fame, this docuseries pulls back the curtain on how The Real Housewives became a cultural phenomenon.

📺 Premieres January 1 | 8–11PM ET/PT on TLC
